"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-paris-2024-organisers-working-on-putting-olympic-flame-on-eiffel-tower-source\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  PARIS, May 22: Paris 2024 organisers have been working on installing the Olympic flame on the Eiffel Tower, a source with direct knowledge of the matter told Reuters on Monday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999856810379415, \"rank\": 1.431833581480749e-05, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not clear whether the flame would stay on the iconic monument throughout the July 26-Aug. 11 sports extravaganza.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The source added that the flame would not be put at the top of the Eiffel Tower, however, for technical reasons.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a work in progress for the last two years now,\\\" the source said.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The flame cannot be at the top of the tower because of the antennas already installed there, they added.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_masts_and_towers\", \"score\": 0.9509173049454505, \"rank\": 0.0516072183788053, \"text\": \"antennas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_masts_and_towers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_masts_and_towers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The venue for the lighting of the flame on the Opening Day of the Olympic Games has not yet been decided,\\\" a Paris 2024 spokesperson told Reuters.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 732,